                <h4 data-uuid="b7ac184941004a4eb4339025d4b54e03">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="02e5b209d9a949f7bc0a7225599d1035">The nation faced difficult challenges during
                    President Bush’s second term.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="6d4b2c9f0be54b31b3d1472e17af3690">George
                    W. Bush</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="eb6cba768be848dfb467bd64575b05ba"></div>
                <section class="graphic-organizer-prompt " data-uuid="35d6c113ef144d43b3e51e7e789abc65">
                    <div class="go-prompt-bottom-bar" data-uuid="fb41460f65bb43d384c7d0ba217cd076">
                        <p data-uuid="ed98d487f10348d0a020eee8f5276df9">As you
                            read, use the graphic organizer to take notes on the domestic and foreign
                            challenges that presidents George W. Bush and Barack Obama faced.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </article>
