                <h5 data-uuid="97dd3622905e47e2ac642e0f2da0d268">Hurricane Katrina<br />
                </h5>
                <p class="caption" data-uuid="43f20e660891456e8adb1ce593fbcc3f">Most of New Orleans was flooded after Hurricane Katrina struck in 2005. Air Force Reserve rescue teams used helicopters to search flooded streets for survivors.</p>
            </div>
