        <p data-uuid="26062483e924433fbc9b5e1a20e40e14">President Bush became less popular as the Iraq War
            continued and the U.S. economy weakened. The financial markets collapsed in the
            fall of 2008, causing an economic recession. At this point, more than
            two-thirds of Americans disapproved of Bush administration policies.</p>
